About Glamour

Welcome to Glamour Beauty Salon & Spa, where luxury meets expertise. Located in the vibrant Glen Austin area of Midrand, we've been transforming looks and boosting confidence for over a decade.

Our team of certified professionals specializes in creating personalized beauty experiences that reflect your unique style and personality. From cutting-edge hair techniques to innovative nail artistry, we stay ahead of the latest trends while maintaining the highest standards of hygiene and customer care.

  • Expert stylists with international training
  • Premium quality products and equipment
  • Personalized consultation for every client
  • Professional nail technician courses
  • Bridal and special event packages
Explore Services

Our Philosophy: Beauty Beyond the Surface

At Glamour, we believe true beauty radiates from within. Our philosophy centers on empowering our clients, not just transforming their appearance. We combine meticulous craftsmanship with a deep understanding of individual needs, fostering a comfortable and uplifting environment where every visit leaves you feeling refreshed, confident, and truly glamorous.

We are dedicated to continuous learning, adopting sustainable practices, and using only ethically sourced, high-quality products to ensure your beauty regimen is as responsible as it is stunning.
